UML:TaggedValue.value: A package of utility elements that are not specific to Geoscience.

1. For GeoSciML purposes gml:name must be used for any identifier or name that is significant beyond the document scope
Metadata elements used from ISO19115 will be implemented using a local XML namespace pending implementation of GeoSciML in GML 3.2. This is because ISO19115 schema require GML 3.2.
